name: INVocabularyStringType
desc: Possible usages for a custom vocabulary term.

items.name: case contactName
items.desc: The name of an app-specific contact.

items.name: case contactGroupName
items.desc: The name of a group of contacts, as a person would say it.

items.name: case photoTag
items.desc: A user-defined keyword associated with an image or images.

items.name: case photoAlbumName
items.desc: The user-given name assigned to a collection of photographs.

items.name: case workoutActivityName
items.desc: The user-given name assigned to a workout.

items.name: case carProfileName
items.desc: The name of a vehicle configuration profile.

items.name: case carName
items.desc: A name that identifies the user’s car.

items.name: case paymentsOrganizationName
items.desc: The name of the bank or company that holds the user’s account.

items.name: case paymentsAccountNickname
items.desc: The user-given nickname for a bank account.

items.name: case notebookItemTitle
items.desc: The title of a note, task, or task list.

items.name: case notebookItemGroupName
items.desc: The title of a group (or folder) containing the user’s notes or task lists.

items.name: case mediaPlaylistTitle
items.desc: The name or title of a playlist.

items.name: case mediaMusicArtistName
items.desc: The name of a musical artist.

items.name: case mediaAudiobookTitle
items.desc: The name or title of an audiobook.

items.name: case mediaAudiobookAuthorName
items.desc: The name of an audiobook’s author.

items.name: case mediaShowTitle
items.desc: The name or title of a podcast or radio show.
